{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory79.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Lee, Kamui, have you found anything?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Sorry, nothing here.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Me neither. There's no one else around apart from us.", 4: '3'}
{3: 'Lucia opened her system menu. It clearly showed a team of four.'}
{3: 'Lucia, Lee, Liv, and Kamui.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Liv, where are you...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Everybody seemed to wake up at different times. Whether this was the system setting or an error was still unknown.'}
{3: "Before three of them woke up, they had all heard Liv's slightly panicking voice."}
{3: 'But Lucia couldn\'t do anything, because she didn\'t have a "body" in the game yet.'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'How strange... Kamui, did you hear anything from Celica? Like, does this game purposely separate team members from one another?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Never... But Liv's HP still looks good on the menu. I don't think she is in danger yet.", 4: '3'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Yeah, indeed.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Kamui did have a point, Lucia thought. This was a game world after all, maybe Liv was just caught up in a special event.'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'What do we do now, Lucia? Shall we follow the instructions and go to the castle?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Let's follow the guide. We might be able to find clues about Liv on the way. ", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Let's beat the monsters and leave the spawn point first!", 4: '3'}
